targets=Ywesee.Software
text=! About ywesee GmbH%0a%0aywesee GmbH is an OpenSource Software company with a bias for OpenStandards and a dedicated focus on the HealthCare industry. We strive to bring HealthCare costs down and we try to communicate as open as possible. You will always find our latest news on ywesee.com. We also do Software that is not directly related to the HealthCare industry. Our projects are done in Ruby, Java and Objective C. For more details about our projects please see the left panel labeled [[Software]].%0a%0aIf you got any question, [[http://www.ywesee.com/pmwiki.php/Ywesee/Kontakt | call]] us or contact us via [[http://www.ywesee.com/pmwiki.php/Ywesee/Kontakt | Email]].
