diff:1245220046:1245219957:=3,4c3,4%0a%3c ywesee GmbH is an OpenSource Software company with a bias for OpenStandards and a dedicated focus on the HealthCare industry. We strive to bring HealthCare costs down and we try to communicate as open as possible. You will always find our latest news on ywesee.com. We also do Software that is not directly related to the HealthCare industry. All our projects are done in Ruby. For more details about our projects please see the left panel labeled [[Software]].%0a%3c %0a---%0a> ywesee GmbH is an OpenSource Software company with a bias for OpenStandards and a dedicated focus on the HealthCare industry. We strive to bring HealthCare costs down and we try to communicate as open as possible. You will always find our latest news on ywesee.com. We also do Software that is not directly related to the HealthCare industry. All our projects are done in Ruby. For more details about our projects please see the left panel labeled "Software".%0a> %0a
