diff:1245157042:1245156981:=3,5c3%0a%3c ywesee GmbH is an OpenSource Software company with a dedicated focus on the HealthCare industry. We strive to bring HealthCare costs down and we try to communicate as open as possible. You will always find our latest news on ywesee.com. We also do Software that is not directly related to the HealthCare industry. All our projects are done in Ruby. For more details about our projects please see the left panel labeled "Software".%0a%3c %0a%3c If you got any question, call us or contact us via Email.%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a---%0a> ywesee GmbH is an OpenSource Software company with a dedicated focus on the HealthCare industry. We strive to bring HealthCare costs down and we try to communicate as open as possible. You will always find our latest news on ywesee.com. We also do Software that is not directly related to the HealthCare industry. All our projects are done in Ruby. For more details about our projects please see the left panel labeled "Software".%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
